		<td><b>Expanding MBC2 ROM to 512kb</b></td>
	</tr>
	<tr>
		<td colspan="2"><hr class="sep" />I know technically the MBC2 can't support more than 256kb, but it's possible to expand NES games beyond their mapper limitations and still have them work on an emulator or a flashcart.<br /><br />My question is if I expanded an MBC2 ROM to 512kb, could I access that additional 256kb of space. Would it work on a flashcart like the Everdrive? etc.

		

		</td>
	</tr>
	</table>


	<hr width="85%" />

	<table width="85%" cellspacing="3" cellpadding="0" border="0" align="center">
	<tr>
